FBIS3-34276 "drnes025_n_94005" FBIS-NES-94-025 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Feb 1994 LEBANON Roundup of 4-7 Feb Clashes in Southern Region Areas Come Under Shelling NC0602071094 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 0615 GMT 6 Feb 94 NC0602071094 Beirut Voice of Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Our correspondent in al-Nabatiyah reports that the Nab' al-Safi basin, Wadi al-Akhdar, and the outskirts of 'Arab Salim came under intermittent artillery fire at dawn today. The shelling was accompanied by bursts of heavy-machine-gun fire from al-Suwayda' hill. The shelling took place following an attack launched by a resistance group against al-Suwayda' post in which rockets and automatic weapons were used.
